Class MapLoader

  • java.lang.Object
    • mapeditor.MapLoader
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IMapLoader

    public class MapLoader
extends java.lang.Object
implements IMapLoader
    This class loads the map into data structures. This loaded information is passed to the editor, and is used to accept user modifications And later save the data from data structures to file as map.
    Author:
    Nikitha Papani, Dinesh Pattapu
